# Scraper / ETL Conventions

- Discovery via the boardexams.ph WordPress REST API; national stats via regex;
  school tables via HTML first, then Playwright + Claude OCR fallback.
- Write through `db.py` only. Every write is an idempotent upsert with an
  `on_conflict` matching the table's UNIQUE key. No raw duplicate inserts.
- Normalize school names with `normalize.py` before insert to keep `schools`
  deduplicated.
- Wrap each program/year run in an import job (`db.start_import_job` /
  `db.finish_import_job`) and write an `audit` entry for significant changes.
- Do NOT scrape or store the full passer roll — only national stats, per-school
  performance, and Top 10 topnotchers.
- After scraping, run `consistency.py` to recompute Consistency Scores.
